How do you ensure the generated shorts are correct?

Answer

Before finalizing the shorts, I implemented a validation step. The system presents the generated clips to the user so they can review them before final output. The user can accept, delete, or modify the segments, ensuring that the final shorts accurately represent the intended content.

What was the biggest challenge in this project?

Answer

One of the biggest challenges was the processing time required to generate the final short clips. When multiple clips need to be created from the video, generating them one by one can take more time. Since these clipping tasks are independent of each other, I applied parallel processing for the final shorts generation. This allowed multiple clips to be created simultaneously, which significantly reduced the total processing time.


